The graph of $y = \sin 5x$ passes through one full period as $5x$ ranges from $0$ to $2\pi$, which means $x$ ranges from $0$ to $\boxed{\frac{2\pi}{5}}.$

The graph of $y = \sin 5x$ is shown below:

